00:14:25.359 --> 00:14:28.400
Second, it defines channels where transactions occur,

00:14:29.119 --> 00:14:32.640
online banking, mobile app, ATM, branch, and point of sale.

00:14:33.760 --> 00:14:38.400
Third, it includes a list of merchants with their merchant category codes

00:14:38.400 --> 00:14:43.760
like Amazon with MCC-5411 for grocery stores

00:14:43.760 --> 00:14:48.239
or Shell Gas with MCC-5541 for gas stations.

00:14:49.119 --> 00:14:52.320
And fourth, it generates realistic transaction amounts

00:14:52.320 --> 00:14:54.159
using a log-normal distribution.

00:14:54.880 --> 00:14:57.200
Most transactions are small, under $100,

00:14:58.239 --> 00:15:02.400
